Id: us-safr-hrd-supply-days-example-codes
Title: "US SAFR Time Period Rantes Value Set"
Description: "This value set uses codes from ISO 8601 for expressing time period ranges."
* ^experimental = true
* http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/time-period-ranges#P0D--0D "0 DAYS"
* http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/time-period-ranges#P1D--3D "1-3 DAYS"
* http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/time-period-ranges#P4D--6D "4-6 DAYS"
* http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/time-period-ranges#P7D--14D "7-14 DAYS"
* http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/time-period-ranges#P15D--30D "15-30 DAYS"
* http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/time-period-ranges#P30D--9999D ">30 DAYS"